In this game a robot shoots a ball at targets. When a target is hit it disappears and reappears in a new location. You get points based on how many targets you hit - 10 points per target.

------------
| CONTROLS |
------------
MENU:
start game - Enter/Return
pause - p

MOVEMENT:
left - a
right - d
forward - w
backward -s
sprint - hold_left_shift
jump - spacebar
shoot - left mouse button 

VIEW:
hold_v - enter first person mode



